git/tig 中文乱码问题：
git config --global core.quotepath false

intall the latest git using apt-get:
  sudo add-apt-repository ppa:git-core/ppa
  sudo apt-get update
  sudo apt-get install git

install git with source code:
  autoconf
  ./configure --prefix=/usr
  make
  sudo make install


# change git push repo:
git remote set-url --push origin git@github.com:user/proj.git
or
git remote set-url --push origin https://github.com/user/proj.git (but will be asked to enter username and password)
